{"tid":2374852,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"姓吳警員太子站偷拍女高級督察裙底 被控遊蕩及意圖妨礙司法公正罪 明早西九龍法院提堂","createTime":"2021-01-21T13:59:36.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-21T16:21:10.000Z","uid":240362,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"72c02f4fe8d609240656b7a03c4c49ba45db1a40","tid":2374852,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-21T13:59:36.000Z","msg":"去年8月25日太子站發生一宗警員偷拍女同袍裙底的案件，一名37歲女高級督察在通往A出口的扶手電梯上被一名男子用手機偷拍裙底，警方調查後以涉嫌遊蕩拘捕該名姓吳（28歲）男子，並揭發他為一名警員。消息指，受害的女高級督察駐守投訴警察課，而涉案警則隸屬東九龍交通部執行及管制組，警方諮詢法律意見後，他已被控以一項「遊蕩」罪及一項「意圖妨礙司法公正」罪，案件將於明日（22日）上午於西九龍裁判法院提堂。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/breaking/20210121/5PECHVQRINBS7FCULKEABQWZX4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20210121%2F5PECHVQRINBS7FCULKEABQWZX4%2F&d=PT6dGXJ5JuBAxmbDRmxpcKtywrPEU2nSstxgUPIv8k8%3D&h=ca91bcd4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20210121%2F5PECHVQRINBS7FCULKEABQWZX4%2F&h=ab2aa9f0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/breaking/20210121/5PECHVQRINBS7FCULKEABQWZX4/</a>"},{"pid":"3887ba537a44c320de4e429e1bfd88dc49466440","tid":2374852,"uid":76804,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-21T14:00:25.000Z","msg":"真係求其捉個罪犯都可以係狗黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"acc1ce355f1f384380124ddd024c304c5320c0c5","tid":2374852,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-21T14:01:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/gun.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/gun.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/gun.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd4f9c2078dcc60e6f9ac8315c8b0d34d3b6373a","tid":2374852,"uid":51752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-21T14:02:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"41a2049004e2c2141d55c1b3181c5a9e6